rong> 801 S Chester St, Little Rock, AR<br><strong>\ud83d\udd50 Hours:</strong> Mon\u2013Sat 12:30 PM \u2013 7:30 PM<br><strong>\ud83d\udcde Phone:</strong> (501) 551-5944</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 28px;font-size:12px;color:#888;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid #eee;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">The Utopia Deli \u00b7 801 S Chester St, Little Rock, AR 72202</p><p style=\"margin:0;\"><a href=\"https://n8n.systack.net/webhook/unsubscribe?email=%%EMAIL%%\" style=\"color:#754681;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe from emails</a> \u00b7 Reply STOP to opt out of texts</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
    sms_body: "Meal prep closes TODAY at 12PM 🤍 Pickup Thu at the deli. Made fresh — grab yours: order.theutopiadeli.com Reply STOP to opt out.",
  },
  friday: {
    email_subject: "Weekend special + behind the scenes at Utopia",
    email_body: "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><title>Weekend special + behind the scenes at Utopia</title></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f8f6f4;font-family:Georgia,serif;\"><table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background:#f8f6f4;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 16px;\"><table width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:#590B3F;padding:24px;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://order.theutopiadeli.com/images/logo.png\" alt=\"The Utopia Deli\" style=\"height:48px;width:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;\"></td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"https://order.theutopiadeli.com/images/cowboy_chicken.webp\" alt=\"The Cowboy Chik'n \u2014 made fresh since 4am Thursday\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;max-height:280px;object-fit:cover;\"></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:32px 28px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;color:#590B3F;font-size:22px;font-family:Georgia,serif;\">How we started making boxes at 4am \ud83e\udd0d</h2><div style=\"color:#333;line-height:1.6;\"><p>Every Thursday morning, we're in the kitchen by 4am prepping meal prep boxes. Not because we have to \u2014 because we committed to everyone who ordered before Wednesday noon.</p><p><strong>Weekend special:</strong> [INSERT SPECIAL] \u2014 available Fri-Sat while it lasts.</p><p>Appreciate you,<br>The Utopia Deli</p></div><p style=\"margin:24px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://order.theutopiadeli.com/pickup-order/\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#AF3D4B;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\">Order Now</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 28px;\"><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #e8e4e0;margin:0;\"></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 28px;background:#faf8f6;font-size:13px;color:#666;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\"><strong>\ud83d\udccd Pickup:</strong> 801 S Chester St, Little Rock, AR<br><strong>\ud83d\udd50 Hours:</strong> Mon\u2013Sat 12:30 PM \u2013 7:30 PM<br><strong>\ud83d\udcde Phone:</strong> (501) 551-5944</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 28px;font-size:12px;color:#888;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid #eee;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">The Utopia Deli \u00b7 801 S Chester St, Little Rock, AR 72202</p><p style=\"margin:0;\"><a href=\"https://n8n.systack.net/webhook/unsubscribe?email=%%EMAIL%%\" style=\"color:#754681;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe from emails</a> \u00b7 Reply STOP to opt out of texts</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
    sms_body: "Weekend special coming 🤍 Plus we're in the kitchen by 4am every Thursday making your meal prep boxes. Come see us: order.theutopiadeli.com Reply STOP to opt out.",
  }
};

// MMS images per day (ready for v2 activation)
const mmsImages = {
  monday: 'https://order.theutopiadeli.com/images/mealprep-mediterranean.jpg',
  wednesday: 'https://order.theutopiadeli.com/images/mealprep-smokey-taco.jpg',
  friday: 'https://order.theutopiadeli.com/images/Deli%20Happy%20customer%20lady.jpg'
};

const template = templates[day] || templates.monday;
const results = [];

for (const item of $input.all()) {
  const c = item.json;

  if (c.email && !c.unsubscribed_email) {
    results.push({
      json: {
        contact_id: c.id,
        channel: 'email',
        to: c.email,
        subject: template.email_subject,
        body: template.email_body.replace(/%%EMAIL%%/g, c.email),
        campaign_day: day
      }
    });
  }

  if (c.phone && !c.unsubscribed_sms) {
    results.push({
      json: {
        contact_id: c.id,
        channel: 'sms',
        to: c.phone,
        body: template.sms_body,
        campaign_day: day,
        media_url: mmsImages[day] || null
      }
    });
  }
}

return results;
